io.sphere.sdk.models

Class LocalizedStrings

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.sphere.sdk.models.Base
      • io.sphere.sdk.models.LocalizedStrings

  • public class LocalizedStrings
extends Base
    A wrapper around an attribute which can be translated into a number of locales. Note that even if your project only uses one language some attributes (name and description for example) will be always be LocalizedStrings.
